    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is definitely in need of some major TLC and mechanical attention, but it represents a fantastic opportunity for a dedicated hobbyist or anyone looking for a donor car for parts. It's a true diamond in the rough waiting for the right person to bring it back to its former glory!",
